FBIS3-34006 "drnes023dd_94006" FBIS-NES-94-023 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Feb 1994 Palestinian Affairs PLO Appoints New Educational Department Head TA0302053294 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 2 Feb 94 TA0302053294 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 2 Feb 94 Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] An informed Palestinian source in Tunis told our correspondent Yoni Ben-Menahem that Palestinian writer Yahya Yakhluf has been appointed director general of the PLO Educational Department, replacing 'Abdallah Hurani, who resigned from the PLO Executive Committee a few months ago.
